<i>noun</i>: 무사태평 [무사태평], 낙천주의 [낙천주의/낙천주이], 낙관주의 [낙꽌주의/낙꽌주이], 낙관론 [낙꽌논], 낙관 [낙꽌] <br>
<ul style="list-style-type:square">
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt>무사태평 [무사태평]</dt><br>
<dd>1. peace; tranquility</dd><br>
<dd>아무런 문제나 걱정거리가 없이 편안함.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of being peaceful without any problem or worry.</dd><br>
<dd>2. optimism</dd><br>
<dd>어떤 일을 심각하게 생각하지 않아 근심이나 걱정이 없음.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of having no worry or concern because one does not think seriously of a matter.</dd><br>
<dt>낙천주의 [낙천주의/낙천주이]</dt><br>
<dd>optimism</dd><br>
<dd>세상과 인생을 즐겁고 좋게 생각하는 태도나 생각.</dd><br>
<dd>A thought or an attitude toward the world and life, which is positive and hopeful.</dd><br>
<dt>낙관주의 [낙꽌주의/낙꽌주이]</dt><br>
<dd>optimism</dd><br>
<dd>세상일을 희망적으로 바라보는 생각이나 태도.</dd><br>
<dd>A thought or an attitude toward the world, which is positive and hopeful.</dd><br>
<dt>낙관론 [낙꽌논]</dt><br>
<dd>optimism</dd><br>
<dd>세상일을 희망적으로 생각하는 견해.</dd><br>
<dd>The attitude of viewing the world with hope.</dd><br>
<dt>낙관 [낙꽌]</dt><br>
<dd>1. optimism</dd><br>
<dd>인생이나 세상을 긍정적이고 희망적으로 봄.</dd><br>
<dd>The attitude of viewing the world or life positively with hope.</dd><br>
<dd>2. optimism</dd><br>
<dd>앞날의 일이 잘 될 것이라고 믿음.</dd><br>
<dd>A belief that things will go well in the future.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>